Package org.patneu.simpleflash

This package currently provides all functionality of the application.

See: Description

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    AboutActivity
    An Activity providing the user access to meta information about the application.
    CameraOnNotification
    A helper class used to provide instances of the standard Notification that this application sends to the user.
    SettingsActivity
    An Activity providing the user access to the settings that are advanced or too unimportant to be shown by the SimpleFlash main class.
    SimpleFlash
    The main class of this application that handles most of it's functionality (or at least delegates it to it's inner classes).
